{"tid":2059269,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"張文寶：「你食屎啦，我唔係中國人呀」","createTime":"2020-06-10T19:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T21:30:18.000Z","uid":129340,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"edebf226793bbd3a748c2c63de6b934cf9206cb0","tid":2059269,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T19:55:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/張文寶\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E5%BC%B5%E6%96%87%E5%AF%B6&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRLyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=f28c1370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/張文寶</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n2012年9月15日，在光復上水的反水貨客示威中，在場警員勸止張文寶與水貨客紛爭時說「大家都係中國人」，張文寶聞言激動反駁：「你食屎！我唔係中國人，你先係中國人呀！」，同日，張文寶在場對水貨客大喊「支那人」而被水貨客情緒激動下掌摑。全程被電視媒體錄像轉播，結果截圖亦廣為流傳。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n2015年8月17日晚上，泰國曼谷四面佛旅遊區發生爆炸事件，兩名香港女生喪生。<br />\n一名名為Ray Cheung的網民，在網上發布言論，指其中一名死者陳詠釿的母親，是警隊前高級督察。他更稱：「為左彰顯我 既仁善，我希望佢係炸到粉身碎骨咁死啦。如果係被火焰燒傷致死我都覺得佢好慘/_\\。做得差人個女就預左&hellip;..遲早要還/_\\」。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde0ae579fd9bc0be9c5583556acda8df0e24c23","tid":2059269,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T20:00:17.000Z","msg":"走得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87948fc293abaed6264a46c66a0de370f04ae7ea","tid":2059269,"uid":227271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T21:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKXi8x3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKXi8x3.gif&h=89c1f1d4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}